  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*BaxterMatrix: build O[u^k]=κ1 a(u)(u+h)^k + κ2 Qθ[u](u-h)^k - τ0(u) u^k for k=0..M.\n  HARD ASSERT that the degree M+1 and M+2 coefficients vanish (this is where a wrong a/d/τ or a\n  wrong ee1=λ1+λ2-M convention would show up). Then columns = degree-0..M coefficients.\n  Used TWICE downstream: (old role) never diagonalized directly anymore; (new role) as the FIXED\n  linear operator whose nullspace at a KNOWN genuine J gives the Q-function coefficients\n  (see QSolve below) — this is now a linear solve, not an eigenvalue problem.*)\nClearAll[BaxterMatrix];\nBaxterMatrix[λ1_, λ2_, M_] := Module[{clists, high, maxhigh, cols},\n  clists = Table[\n     PadRight[\n      CoefficientList[\n       Expand[κ1 aFun[λ1, λ2][u] (u + h)^k + κ2 Qθ[u] (u - h)^k - τ0[λ1, λ2, M][u] u^k],\n       u],\n      M + 3],\n     {k, 0, M}];\n  high = clists[[All, {M + 2, M + 3}]];   (* degree M+1 and M+2 coeffs for each column k *)\n  maxhigh = Max[Abs[Flatten[high]]];\n  If[maxhigh > 10^-18,\n    Print[\"BaxterMatrix ASSERTION FAILED (λ1,λ2,M)=\", {λ1, λ2, M},\n          \"  max|high-degree coeff|=\", maxhigh, \"  high=\", high];\n    Abort[]];\n  cols = clists[[All, 1 ;; M + 1]];       (* degrees 0..M, one column per k *)\n  Transpose[cols]\n];\nDimensions /@ (BaxterMatrix[1, 1, #] & /@ {0, 1, 2})",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1013\" data-out-n=\"62\" data-sub-idx=\"3\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"30\" data-sub-start=\"24\" data-sub-end=\"24\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[62]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqpxp9x-m6kht9n\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGJlZ2lue3BtYXRyaXh9MSAmIDFcXDIgJiAyXFwzICYgM1xlbmR7cG1hdHJpeH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:3.6em;vertical-align:-1.55em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.05em;\"><span style=\"top:-4.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:5.6em;\"></span><span style=\"width:0.875em;height:3.600em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.875em\" height=\"3.600em\" viewBox=\"0 0 875 3600\"><path d=\"M863,9c0,-2,-2,-5,-6,-9c0,0,-17,0,-17,0c-12.7,0,-19.3,0.3,-20,1\nc-5.3,5.3,-10.3,11,-15,17c-242.7,294.7,-395.3,682,-458,1162c-21.3,163.3,-33.3,349,\n-36,557 l0,84c0.2,6,0,26,0,60c2,159.3,10,310.7,24,454c53.3,528,210,\n949.7,470,1265c4.7,6,9.7,11.7,15,17c0.7,0.7,7,1,19,1c0,0,18,0,18,0c4,-4,6,-7,6,-9\nc0,-2.7,-3.3,-8.7,-10,-18c-135.3,-192.7,-235.5,-414.3,-300.5,-665c-65,-250.7,-102.5,\n-544.7,-112.5,-882c-2,-104,-3,-167,-3,-189\nl0,-92c0,-162.7,5.7,-314,17,-454c20.7,-272,63.7,-513,129,-723c65.3,\n-210,155.3,-396.3,270,-559c6.7,-9.3,10,-15.3,10,-18z\"/></svg></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\"