       "data": "Out[84]= \\left\\{\\left\\{1.000000000000000000000000000+0.\\times 10^{-29}\\,\\mathrm{i},-1.300449488107643627209235814+0.\\times 10^{-29}\\,\\mathrm{i},2.021329238402096701742591115+0.\\times 10^{-29}\\,\\mathrm{i},1.\\,+0.\\times 10^{-29}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right\\},-0.02291660900+0.\\times 10^{-12}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right\\}",
