       "data": "Out[170]= \\langle\\!\\lvert \\text{max spread (ratio non-constancy)}\\to 0.\\,,\\text{max |ratio - 1| over sweep}\\to 0.\\,,\\text{num ($\\lambda$1,$\\lambda$2,s1) cases checked}\\to 27\\rvert\\!\\rangle",
