  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*Section F — functional CG overlap. Sets up the length-1 FSoV measure/bracket (Section C's\n  mu[...][1] stripped of all site-2 factors and the cross-site (1-Exp[...]) term), normalized so\n  br1[λ1][f] = f(θ1) + (higher-tower). Then builds the functional object FL = br1[λ1][k^(u/h) Q1]\n  and the operatorial CG overlap OP = (⟨x0|g(k)⊗⟨x0|)·Psi, and DISCOVERS the dictionary\n  {generator, φ(k), scalar} relating them (exploratory — no predicted formula asserted).\n  NOTE: Q1 carries κ1^(u/h), so k^(u/h) Q1 = (k κ1)^(u/h) q_n(u): the LHS prefactor is (k κ1)^(θ1/h).\n  See docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-16-xxx-sov-factorization-functional-overlap-design.md.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Length-1 FSoV measure and bracket. mu1 is a single-site rational measure with simple poles at\n  the tower θ1+h k, k=0..λ. Nn1 is DERIVED (not guessed) by forcing the θ1-node weight\n  w_0 = 2πI Res[mu1, θ1] to equal 1, so that br1[λ][f] = f(θ1) + (higher-tower). br1 is the residue\n  sum over the whole tower. (For λ≥1 the residues of mu1 sum to 0, so br1[λ][1]=0 — the correct\n  normalization statement is w_0=1, checked next.)*)\nClearAll[Nn1, mu1, br1];\nNn1[λ_] := Nn1[λ] = Module[{uu}, 1/(2 π I Residue[1/Product[(uu - θ1 - h k), {k, 0, λ}], {uu, θ1}])];\nmu1[λ_][u_] := Nn1[λ]/Product[(u - θ1 - h k), {k, 0, λ}];\nbr1[λ_][f_] := 2 π I Plus @@ (Residue[f mu1[λ][u], {u, #}] & /@ Table[θ1 + h k, {k, 0, λ}]);",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Internal check: the leading (θ1-node) weight must be exactly 1 for λ=1,2,3 (this IS the\n  br1[f]=f(θ1)+... normalization), and br1[λ][1] must be 0 (rational-measure residues sum to\n  zero). Also list the full weight vectors w_j for the record.*)\nw1[λ_] := Table[2 π I Residue[mu1[λ][u], {u, θ1 + h j}], {j, 0, λ}];\nNn1Check::badlead = \"Leading weight w_0 ≠ 1 for λ=`1`: w_0=`2`.\";\nNn1Check::badsum = \"br1[λ][1] ≠ 0 for λ=`1`: got `2`.\";\nDo[\n  Module[{w = w1[λ], s},\n   If[Abs[N[w[[1]] - 1]] > 10^-15, Message[Nn1Check::badlead, λ, w[[1]]]; Abort[]];\n   s = br1[λ][1];\n   If[Abs[N[s]] > 10^-15, Message[Nn1Check::badsum, λ, s]; Abort[]]],\n  {λ, 1, 3}];\n<|\"w_0 (λ=1,2,3)\" -> Table[w1[λ][[1]], {λ, 1, 3}],\n  \"full weights w_j\" -> Table[λ -> w1[λ], {λ, 1, 3}],\n  \"br1[λ][1] (λ=1,2,3)\" -> Table[br1[λ][1], {λ, 1, 3}]|>",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1034\" data-out-n=\"185\" data-sub-idx=\"5\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"64\" data-sub-start=\"12\" data-sub-end=\"14\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[185]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqpyc3h-6zqpn00\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.06em;vertical-align:-0.31em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">⟨</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:-0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">∣</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">w_0 (</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">=1,2,3)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.06em;vertical-align:-0.31em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">full weights w_j</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">br1[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">][1] (</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">=1,2,3)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mclose\">∣</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:-0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mclose\">⟩</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[185]= \\langle\\!\\lvert \\text{w\\_0 ($\\lambda$=1,2,3)}\\to \\left\\{1,1,1\\right\\},\\text{full weights w\\_j}\\to \\left\\{1\\to \\left\\{1,-1\\right\\},2\\to \\left\\{1,-2,1\\right\\},3\\to \\left\\{1,-3,3,-1\\right\\}\\right\\},\\text{br1[$\\lambda$][1] ($\\lambda$=1,2,3)}\\to \\left\\{0,0,0\\right\\}\\rvert\\!\\rangle",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "4fbab9b0-82ce-45d1-9089-ed20de692197"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Sanity: br1 acting on a generic analytic f reproduces the weighted tower sum Σ_j w_j f(θ1+h j),\n  and picks out f(θ1) as the leading term. Test with f=g[u] (undefined head, stays symbolic).*)\nClear[g];\n{br1[1][g[u]] - Sum[w1[1][[j + 1]] g[θ1 + h j], {j, 0, 1}] // Simplify,\n br1[2][g[u]] - Sum[w1[2][[j + 1]] g[θ1 + h j], {j, 0, 2}] // Simplify}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1035\" data-out-n=\"187\" data-sub-idx=\"2\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"65\" data-sub-start=\"3\" data-sub-end=\"4\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[187]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqpychk-j9xf48j\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezAsMFxyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[187]= \\left\\{0,0\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "ec2010d5-4163-4a11-9b72-da1dee2e4b53"
    }
