  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*Required milestone: the site-2 mirror of Section F's operatorial/functional dictionary. Rotate\nthe SITE-2 pseudovacuum covector instead of site 1's, and check whether det1s2[λ2][k^(u/h)Q1] closes\nagainst (⟨x0[λ1]|⊗⟨x0[λ2]|exp[φ E_ab^(site2)]).Psi under a universal linear rescaling φ(k)=α2 k,\nexactly mirroring Section F's Cells 67-77 but with the roles of the two tensor factors swapped.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*OP2: rotate the SITE-2 pseudovacuum covector by gRot[λ2][a,b][φ] (site 1's covector left bare),\n  contract with the two-site right eigenvector Psi — the site-2 operatorial CG overlap.*)\nClearAll[OP2];\nOP2[λ1_,λ2_][a_,b_][M_,n_][φ_] := Flatten[KroneckerProduct[xSingle[λ1][{0}], xSingle[λ2][{0}].gRot[λ2][a,b][φ]]] . Psi[λ1,λ2][M,n];\n\n(*Which single-site generator on SITE 2 produces genuine φ-dependence? Mirrors Cell 69's test,\n  fixed case (λ1,λ2)=(2,1), state (1,0) — same rep/state used for the site-1 test, this time\n  rotating the site-2 factor instead.*)\nop12s2 = OP2[2,1][1,2][1,0][φ] // Simplify;\nop21s2 = OP2[2,1][2,1][1,0][φ] // Simplify;\ngenNontrivial2 = If[FreeQ[op12s2//Expand,φ] && !FreeQ[op21s2//Expand,φ], {2,1},\n                     If[FreeQ[op21s2//Expand,φ] && !FreeQ[op12s2//Expand,φ], {1,2}, $Failed]];\nIf[genNontrivial2===$Failed, Abort[]];\nClearAll[OPg2];\nOPg2[λ1_,λ2_][M_,n_][φ_] := OP2[λ1,λ2][genNontrivial2[[1]],genNontrivial2[[2]]][M,n][φ];\n{\"OP2(E12)\",op12s2,\"OP2(E21)\",op21s2,\"nontrivial generator {a,b}\",genNontrivial2}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1053\" data-out-n=\"294\" data-sub-idx=\"10\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"88\" data-sub-start=\"15\" data-sub-end=\"15\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[294]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqpz12r-c7pfoba\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.2141em;vertical-align:-0.35em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">{</span></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">OP2(E12)</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">30</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">OP2(E21)</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">2.603469709065218092712489006</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.6885776528619826437114966465</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">φ</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord\">1.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">30</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">)</span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">nontrivial generator {a,b}</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[294]= \\left\\{\\text{OP2(E12)},1.\\,+0.\\times 10^{-30}\\,\\mathrm{i},\\text{OP2(E21)},\\left(2.603469709065218092712489006+0.6885776528619826437114966465\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,\\varphi +\\left(1.\\,+0.\\times 10^{-30}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right),\\text{nontrivial generator \\{a,b\\}},\\left\\{2,1\\right\\}\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "e6ea0842-dafa-4579-9f93-a8fbd49e3f45"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*FLdet2: the site-2 functional CG-overlap object, det1s2 applied to k^(u/h)Q1[λ1,λ2][M,n][u].\n  Since Q1 carries κ1^(u/h) (the SHARED companion-twist eigenvalue, not a site-2-specific one — Q1\n  is a single chain-level Baxter function, not resolved per site) f(θ2)=(kκ1)^(θ2/h)q_n(θ2), and\n  dividing by it cancels the fractional prefactor exactly as for FLdet, leaving a clean degree-λ2\n  polynomial in k.*)\nClearAll[FLdet2];\nFLdet2[λ1_,λ2_][M_,n_][k_] := det1s2[λ2][k^(u/h) Q1[λ1,λ2][M,n][u]];\n(*smoke test: rep (2,1) (λ2=1), state (0,0) — should be linear in k, constant term 1.*)\nFLdet2[2,1][0,0][k]//Simplify",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1054\" data-out-n=\"297\" data-sub-idx=\"4\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"89\" data-sub-start=\"8\" data-sub-end=\"8\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[297]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqpz1h6-es0s9nn\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnQoMS5cLCswLlx0aW1lcyAxMF57LTI3fVwsXG1hdGhybXtpfVxyaWdodCktXGxlZnQoMC4zNjA0Mzk4NzUxNDcyMjY1MzcyNjY2Nzc2NTErMC45MzI3ODI0NDg1OTMzNzQ3MTY0ODQ4MzU5ODJcLFxtYXRocm17aX1ccmlnaHQpXCxr\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.2141em;vertical-align:-0.35em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord\">1.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">27</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">)</span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">0.360439875147226537266677651</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.932782448593374716484835982</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[297]= \\left(1.\\,+0.\\times 10^{-27}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)-\\left(0.360439875147226537266677651+0.932782448593374716484835982\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k",
       "mime": "text/plain"
