       "data": "Out[316]= \\left\\{\\text{Fcand1},k1^2\\,\\left(\\left(-2.2527492196701659-5.82989030370859198\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k2-\\left(0.4170744170089964+23.0487337186617355\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\right)+k1\\,\\left(\\left(0.67128913890100625-0.37524873225652243\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k2+\\left(9.51343802264711551-1.5262799733212005\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\right)-\\left(1.99115021541939352-0.72828474168870538\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k2+\\left(1.000000000000000000+0.\\times 10^{-18}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right),\\text{O2rot},k1^2\\,\\left(\\left(-0.3604398751472265372666776506-0.9327824485933747164848359821\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k2-\\left(0.03626734060947795145020244939+2.004237714666237867354326095\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\right)+k1\\,\\left(\\left(1.296101147801774460249890292+2.676661693287278344489306162\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k2+\\left(1.522150083623538480912456055-0.2442047957313920727733393355\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\right)-\\left(2.603469709065218092712489006+0.6885776528619826437114966465\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k2+\\left(1.\\,+0.\\times 10^{-30}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\right\\}",
