/span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:5.65em;\"><span style=\"top:-1.366em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:5.616em;\"></span><span class=\"delimsizinginner delim-size4\"><span>⎭</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-1.358em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:5.616em;\"></span><span style=\"height:3.616em;width:0.8889em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.8889em\" height=\"3.616em\" style=\"width:0.8889em\" viewBox=\"0 0 888.89 3616\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin\"><path d=\"M384 0 H504 V3616 H384z M384 0 H504 V3616 H384z\"/></svg></span></span><span style=\"top:-5.616em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:5.616em;\"></span><span class=\"delimsizinginner delim-size4\"><span>⎬</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-6.758em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:5.616em;\"></span><span style=\"height:3.616em;width:0.8889em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.8889em\" height=\"3.616em\" style=\"width:0.8889em\" viewBox=\"0 0 888.89 3616\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin\"><path d=\"M384 0 H504 V3616 H384z M384 0 H504 V3616 H384z\"/></svg></span></span><span style=\"top:-10.366em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:5.616em;\"></span><span class=\"delimsizinginner delim-size4\"><span>⎫</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:5.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[364]= \\left\\{\\text{STEP 1 CONFIRMED: ⟨x0[$\\lambda$]|E21\\^{}m = $\\gamma$\\_m($\\lambda$) xL1[$\\lambda$][\\{m\\}], $\\gamma$\\_m($\\lambda$)=$\\lambda$!/($\\lambda$-m)!},\\text{worst deviation},0,\\text{table \\{$\\lambda$,m,$\\gamma$\\_found,$\\gamma$\\_predicted,dev\\}},\\begin{pmatrix}1 & 0 & 1.\\, & 1 & 0\\\\1 & 1 & 1.\\, & 1 & 0\\\\2 & 0 & 1.\\, & 1 & 0\\\\2 & 1 & 2.\\, & 2 & 0\\\\2 & 2 & 2.\\, & 2 & 0\\\\3 & 0 & 1.\\, & 1 & 0\\\\3 & 1 & 3.\\, & 3 & 0\\\\3 & 2 & 6.\\, & 6 & 0\\\\3 & 3 & 6.\\, & 6 & 0\\end{pmatrix}\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "6434113f-53c7-4245-8ea2-6ab5597d8224"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*STEP 2 (the crux) — does the s2=m slice of the two-site SoV basis factorize the SAME way\n  Section E proved for m=0: x2[λ1,λ2][{s1,m}] =? xL1[λ1][{s1}] ⊗ xL1[λ2][{m}] (using xL1 for BOTH\n  factors — the only level-m single-site covector object this notebook has; per Step 1 this is\n  proportional to ⟨x0[λ2]|E21^m by the known γ_m(λ2)). Test constancy of the componentwise ratio\n  over nonzero entries, m=1..λ2 (m=0 already proven, Section E Cell 60), for every (λ1,λ2,s1,m) in\n  the sweep λ1,λ2∈{1,2,3}.*)\nClearAll[step2Report];\nstep2Report = {};\nDo[\n  Do[\n    Do[\n      Module[{lhs,rhsraw,ratios,spread,ratioVal},\n        lhs = Flatten[x2[λ1,λ2][{s1,m}]];\n        rhsraw = Flatten[KroneckerProduct[xL1[λ1][{s1}], xL1[λ2][{m}]]];\n        ratios = Table[If[Chop[rhsraw[[i]],10^-12]===0, Nothing, lhs[[i]]/rhsraw[[i]]], {i,Length[lhs]}];\n        ratios = N[ratios];\n        spread = If[Length[ratios]>1, Max[Abs[ratios-ratios[[1]]]], 0];\n        ratioVal = If[Length[ratios]>0, ratios[[1]], Missing[\"NoNonzero\"]];\n        AppendTo[step2Report, {λ1,λ2,s1,m, Chop[ratioVal,10^-10], Chop[spread,10^-10]}]\n      ]\n    ,{m,1,λ2}]\n  ,{s1,0,λ1}]\n,{λ1,{1,2,3}},{λ2,{1,2,3}}];\nworstSpread2 = Max[step2Report[[All,6]]];\n{\"STEP 2: x2[{s1,m}] vs xL1[λ1][{s1}]⊗xL1[λ2][{m}], worst ratio-spread (constancy check)\", worstSpread2,\n \"num cases\", Length[step2Report], \"sample rows\", Take[step2Report,UpTo[10]]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
