  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*STEP 2 RESOLUTION: the mixing found above is confined to states of FIXED TOTAL LEVEL L=s1+m —\n  not a simple triangular s1-only mixing, but a genuine \"same-total-level\" recoupling. Verify this\n  level-conservation property broadly: for every (λ1,λ2,s1,m) in the sweep, decompX2 should have\n  ALL its nonzero coefficients exactly at (s1',m') with s1'+m'=s1+m.*)\nlevelCheck = {};\nDo[\n  Do[\n    Do[\n      Module[{d,offLevel},\n        d = decompX2[λ1,λ2][s1,m];\n        offLevel = Select[d, (#[[2]]=!=0 && #[[1,1]]+#[[1,2]]!=s1+m)&];\n        AppendTo[levelCheck, {λ1,λ2,s1,m, Length[offLevel]}]\n      ]\n    ,{m,0,λ2}]\n  ,{s1,0,λ1}]\n,{rep,{{2,1},{1,2},{2,2},{3,1}}},{λ1,{rep[[1]]}},{λ2,{rep[[2]]}}];\nworstOffLevel = Max[levelCheck[[All,5]]];\n{\"STEP 2 level-conservation check: # off-level nonzero coeffs (want 0 everywhere)\", worstOffLevel,\n \"num (λ1,λ2,s1,m) cases\", Length[levelCheck]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1077\" data-out-n=\"396\" data-sub-idx=\"4\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"116\" data-sub-start=\"17\" data-sub-end=\"18\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[396]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqpzjh8-1da5tc7\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0e1NURVAgMiBsZXZlbC1jb25zZXJ2YXRpb24gY2hlY2s6IFwjIG9mZi1sZXZlbCBub256ZXJvIGNvZWZmcyAod2FudCAwIGV2ZXJ5d2hlcmUpfSwwLFx0ZXh0e251bSAoJFxsYW1iZGEkMSwkXGxhbWJkYSQyLHMxLG0pIGNhc2VzfSwyOVxyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">STEP 2 level-conservation check: # off-level nonzero coeffs (want 0 everywhere)</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">num (</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">1,</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"mord\">2,s1,m) cases</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">29</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[396]= \\left\\{\\text{STEP 2 level-conservation check: \\# off-level nonzero coeffs (want 0 everywhere)},0,\\text{num ($\\lambda$1,$\\lambda$2,s1,m) cases},29\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "66ace617-313b-46ff-adef-3806600bbda1"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*STEP 2 conclusion: the pure rank-1 factorization x2[λ1,λ2][{s1,m}] ∝ xL1[λ1][{s1}]⊗xL1[λ2][{m}]\nholds ONLY at m=0 (Section E) — for m>=1 it fails as a single term, but resolves into a STRUCTURED\ndeviation: x2[λ1,λ2][{s1,m}] decomposes EXACTLY (0 off-level coefficients, 29 cases checked) within\nthe FIXED-TOTAL-LEVEL subspace span{xL1[λ1][{s1'}]⊗xL1[λ2][{m'}] : s1'+m'=s1+m}, i.e. a genuine\nlevel-graded recoupling (finer than mere s1-triangular mixing) rather than a scalar. Per the stop\ncondition (\"triangular mixing means the det candidates need a linear recombination... still a\nmodified det result\"), STEP 3 is attempted directly against the operatorial graded pieces O_m[k1]\n(extracted as k2-Taylor coefficients of the already-fully-verified O2rot, sidestepping the need to\ninvert the level-mixing analytically) rather than composing it explicitly.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*STEP 3 — graded dictionary. O_m[k1] extracted as (-1)^m m! · (k2^m coefficient of O2rot); this is\n  exact by construction (O2rot is a finite polynomial in k2 of degree λ2). Candidate:\n  Cm[λ1,λ2][M,n][k1] := br[λ1,λ2][1][Pm[u] k1^(u/h) Q1[u]] / NORM, Pm[u]=Product[(u-θ2-hk),{k,0,m-1}]\n  (empty=1 at m=0 — the ALREADY-PROVEN Phase-1 m=λ2+1-equivalent full case is the λ2-degree P1site2,\n  distinct from this partial Pm). Try NORM = value at θ1 (det1-style) first, m=0,1 only (cheapest\n  gate) on rep (2,1) state (1,0).*)\nClearAll[Pm,Om,Cm];\nPm[m_][u_] := Product[(u-θ2-h k),{k,0,m-1}];  (*empty product convention: Product[...,{k,0,-1}]=1*)\nOm[λ1_,λ2_][M_,n_][m_][k1_] := (-1)^m m! Coefficient[O2rot[λ1,λ2][M,n][k1,k2],k2,m];\nCm[λ1_,λ2_][M_,n_][m_][k1_] := Module[{f},\n  f[uu_] := Pm[m][uu] k1^(uu/h) Q1[λ1,λ2][M,n][uu];\n  br[λ1,λ2][1][f[u]] / (f[θ1])\n];\ntestM0 = Simplify[Om[2,1][1,0][0][k1] - Cm[2,1][1,0][0][k1]];\ntestM1raw = Simplify[Om[2,1][1,0][1][k1]];\ntestM1cand = Simplify[Cm[2,1][1,0][1][k1]];\n{\"m=0: Om-Cm (must be 0 per Phase1, C1pred/P1site2[θ1] should equal exactly Cm's own norm here)\", Chop[N[testM0],10^-10],\n \"m=1: Om_1[k1]\", testM1raw, \"m=1: Cm_1[k1]\", testM1cand}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1078\" data-out-n=\"404\" data-sub-idx=\"8\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"118\" data-sub-start=\"16\" data-sub-end=\"17\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[404]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqpzjvz-gk080ab\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.2141em;vertical-align:-0.35em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">{</span></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">m=0: Om-Cm (must be 0 per Phase1, C1pred/P1site2[</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord\">1] should equal exactly Cm’s own norm here)</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">2.5572121404875445 </span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.4102640568287387</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">0.038411844228125346 </span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2.1227491621421546</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">m=1: Om_1[k1]</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">0.3604398751472265372666776506</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.9327824485933747164848359821</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">1.296101147801774460249890292</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2.676661693287278344489306162</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">2.603469709065218092712489006</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.6885776528619826437114966465</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">m=1: Cm_1[k1]</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">0.02466179161444500699</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1.36288164597304174980</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">6.4691378554000385439</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1.0378703818584163093</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord\">1.000000000000000000000</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">21</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">)</span></span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
