       "data": "Out[489]= \\left\\{\\text{Conjectured sum rule FAILS beyond the lucky L=1 case},\\text{num failing cases},29,\\text{num total cases},81,\\text{sample failures},\\begin{pmatrix}1 & 2 & 0 & 1 & \\frac{1}{-\\theta A+\\theta B-1}\\\\1 & 2 & 0 & 2 & \\frac{2}{\\theta A-\\theta B+1}\\\\1 & 3 & 0 & 1 & -\\frac{2}{\\theta A-\\theta B+1}\\end{pmatrix}\\right\\}",
