       "data": "Out[496]= \\left\\{\\text{BOXED: A[s1,m;s1,m] = Pochhammer[s1+$\\theta$1-$\\theta$2-m+1,m]/Pochhammer[$\\lambda$1+$\\theta$1-$\\theta$2-m+1,m] --- verified at the live numeric $\\theta$1,$\\theta$2},\\text{worst deviation},0,\\text{num ($\\lambda$1,$\\lambda$2,s1,m) cases},81\\right\\}",
