  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*Section K — derivation-first closure of the two-rotation formula, following Paul's corrected\nwave-function factorization. STEP 1: verify x2[λ1,λ2][{s1,s2}].Psi[M,n] = Q1(θ1+s1h)Q1(θ2+s2h)/(Q1(θ1)Q1(θ2))\nexactly, hard-asserted across the full 41-state sweep, all (s1,s2). Tests both WITH Q1's own\nκ1^(u/h) twist prefactor (the object actually called Q1 in this notebook) and WITHOUT it (the bare\npolynomial qpoly[QSolve[...],u]), to pin down precisely how/whether the prefactor cancels.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*STEP 1a — test WITH Q1's own κ1^(u/h) prefactor (Q1 as defined in Section B).*)\nClearAll[Wfun,step1TestWith];\nWfun[λ1_,λ2_][M_,n_][s1_,s2_] := Q1[λ1,λ2][M,n][θ1+s1] Q1[λ1,λ2][M,n][θ2+s2] / (Q1[λ1,λ2][M,n][θ1] Q1[λ1,λ2][M,n][θ2]);\nstep1TestWith = {};\nDo[\n  Do[\n    Module[{xv,pred,resid},\n      xv = First[Flatten[x2[λ1,λ2][{s1,s2}] . Psi[λ1,λ2][st[[1]],st[[2]]]]];\n      pred = Wfun[λ1,λ2][st[[1]],st[[2]]][s1,s2];\n      resid = Chop[N[xv-pred],10^-15];\n      AppendTo[step1TestWith, {λ1,λ2,st,s1,s2,resid}]\n    ]\n  ,{s1,0,λ1},{s2,0,λ2}]\n,{rep,{{1,1},{2,1},{1,2},{2,2},{3,1},{1,3}}},{λ1,{rep[[1]]}},{λ2,{rep[[2]]}},{st,statesOf[λ1,λ2]}];\nworstStep1With = Max[Abs[step1TestWith[[All,6]]]];\n{\"STEP 1a (WITH κ1^(u/h) prefactor): worst |x2.Psi - Q1(θ1+s1)Q1(θ2+s2)/(Q1(θ1)Q1(θ2))|\", worstStep1With,\n \"num cases\", Length[step1TestWith]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1094\" data-out-n=\"502\" data-sub-idx=\"6\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"139\" data-sub-start=\"15\" data-sub-end=\"16\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[502]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqpzzf0-wtft1ys\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0e1NURVAgMWEgKFdJVEggJFxrYXBwYSQxXF57fSh1L2gpIHByZWZhY3Rvcik6IHdvcnN0IHx4Mi5Qc2kgLSBRMSgkXHRoZXRhJDErczEpUTEoJFx0aGV0YSQyK3MyKS8oUTEoJFx0aGV0YSQxKVExKCRcdGhldGEkMikpfH0sMCxcdGV4dHtudW0gY2FzZXN9LDI5N1xyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">STEP 1a (WITH </span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">κ</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord accent\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"accent-body\" style=\"left:-0.25em;\"><span class=\"mord\">ˆ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord\">(u/h) prefactor): worst |x2.Psi - Q1(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord\">1+s1)Q1(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord\">2+s2)/(Q1(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord\">1)Q1(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord\">2))|</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">num cases</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">297</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[502]= \\left\\{\\text{STEP 1a (WITH $\\kappa$1\\^{}(u/h) prefactor): worst |x2.Psi - Q1($\\theta$1+s1)Q1($\\theta$2+s2)/(Q1($\\theta$1)Q1($\\theta$2))|},0,\\text{num cases},297\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "4a67aa0d-df5c-4a7d-8b01-47d41ba32bb7"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*STEP 1b — sanity comparison: test WITHOUT the κ1^(u/h) prefactor (bare polynomial q_n(u) only),\n  to explicitly confirm the prefactor is essential (and see how it fails) rather than merely assuming\n  1a's success means the prefactor was irrelevant.*)\nClearAll[qbare,WfunBare,step1TestBare];\nqbare[λ1_,λ2_][M_,n_][u_] := qpoly[QSolve[λ1,λ2][M,n],u];\nWfunBare[λ1_,λ2_][M_,n_][s1_,s2_] := qbare[λ1,λ2][M,n][θ1+s1] qbare[λ1,λ2][M,n][θ2+s2] / (qbare[λ1,λ2][M,n][θ1] qbare[λ1,λ2][M,n][θ2]);\nstep1TestBare = {};\nDo[\n  Module[{xv,pred,resid},\n    xv = First[Flatten[x2[2,1][{s1,s2}] . Psi[2,1][st[[1]],st[[2]]]]];\n    pred = WfunBare[2,1][st[[1]],st[[2]]][s1,s2];\n    resid = Chop[N[xv-pred],10^-15];\n    AppendTo[step1TestBare, {st,s1,s2,resid}]\n  ]\n,{s1,0,2},{s2,0,1},{st,statesOf[2,1]}];\nworstStep1Bare = Max[Abs[step1TestBare[[All,4]]]];\n{\"STEP 1b (WITHOUT prefactor, bare q_n): worst residual (expect NONZERO, confirming prefactor matters)\",\n worstStep1Bare, \"sample\", Take[step1TestBare,UpTo[3]]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1095\" data-out-n=\"509\" data-sub-idx=\"7\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"140\" data-sub-start=\"16\" data-sub-end=\"17\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[509]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqpzzs7-04xcgz8\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:3.6em;vertical-align:-1.55em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.05em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.15em;\"></span><span class=\"delimsizinginner delim-size4\"><span>⎩</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-2.492em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.15em;\"></span><span style=\"height:0.016em;width:0.8889em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.8889em\" height=\"0.016em\" style=\"width:0.8889em\" viewBox=\"0 0 888.89 16\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin\"><path d=\"M384 0 H504 V16 H384z M384 0 H504 V16 H384z\"/></svg></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.15em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.15em;\"></span><span class=\"delimsizinginner delim-size4\"><span>⎨</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-4.292em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.15em;\"></span><span style=\"height:0.016em;width:0.8889em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.8889em\" height=\"0.016em\" style=\"width:0.8889em\" viewBox=\"0 0 888.89 16\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin\"><path d=\"M384 0 H504 V16 H384z M384 0 H504 V16 H384z\"/></svg></span></span><span style=\"top:-4.3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.15em;\"></span><span class=\"delimsizinginner delim-size4\"><span>⎧</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.55em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">STEP 1b (WITHOUT prefactor, bare q_n): worst residual (expect NONZERO, confirming prefactor matters)</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.7396476326262356</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">sample</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.05em;\"><span style=\"top:-4.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:5.6em;\"></span><span style=\"width:0.875em;height:3.600em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.875em\" height=\"3.600em\" viewBox=\"0 0 875 3600\"><path d=\"M863,9c0,-2,-2,-5,-6,-9c0,0,-17,0,-17,0c-12.7,0,-19.3,0.3,-20,1\nc-5.3,5.3,-10.3,11,-15,17c-242.7,294.7,-395.3,682,-458,1162c-21.3,163.3,-33.3,349,\n-36,557 l0,84c0.2,6,0,26,0,60c2,159.3,10,310.7,24,454c53.3,528,210,\n949.7,470,1265c4.7,6,9.7,11.7,15,17c0.7,0.7,7,1,19,1c0,0,18,0,18,0c4,-4,6,-7,6,-9\nc0,-2.7,-3.3,-8.7,-10,-18c-135.3,-192.7,-235.5,-414.3,-300.5,-665c-65,-250.7,-102.5,\n-544.7,-112.5,-882c-2,-104,-3,-167,-3,-189\nl0,-92c0,-162.7,5.7,-314,17,-454c20.7,-272,63.7,-513,129,-723c65.3,\n-210,155.3,-396.3,270,-559c6.7,-9.3,10,-15.3,10,-