   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*STEP 3 — assembly, now UNCONDITIONAL given Steps 1-2 verified exactly:\n   O[k1,k2] = Σ_{a,b} cA[a](k1)cB[b](k2) MP[a,b],  cA[a](k1)=(-k1)^a/a!·γ_a(λ1), cB[b](k2)=(-k2)^b/b!·γ_b(λ2)\n   MP[a,b] = Σ_{s,t:s+t=a+b} B[a,b;s,t] W[s,t],  W[s,t]=Q1(θ1+s)Q1(θ2+t)/(Q1(θ1)Q1(θ2))  (Step 1)\n   This closes BY CONSTRUCTION (B was solved exactly from MP=B.W, a tautology at the level of the\n   states used to solve it) — the real content is verifying it holds for FRESH (k1,k2) values and\n   reproduces the independently-known O2rot exactly, which is the actual hard test.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Memoize solveBrat (it's called many times below) and assemble O[k1,k2].*)\nClearAll[solveBratM,Oassembled];\nsolveBratM[λ1_,λ2_][a_,b_] := solveBratM[λ1,λ2][a,b] = solveBrat[λ1,λ2][a,b];\nOassembled[λ1_,λ2_][M_,n_][k1_,k2_] := Sum[\n  Module[{srng,bv,cA,cB},\n    cA = (-k1)^a/a! gammaFun[λ1,a];\n    cB = (-k2)^b/b! gammaFun[λ2,b];\n    {srng,bv} = solveBratM[λ1,λ2][a,b][[1;;2]];\n    cA cB Sum[bv[[i]] Wval[λ1,λ2][M,n][srng[[i]], a+b-srng[[i]]], {i,Length[srng]}]\n  ]\n,{a,0,λ1},{b,0,λ2}];\n(*hard test: rep (2,1), all 6 states, sampled at 3 independent (k1,k2) grid points.*)\ngridPts = {{1.3,0.7},{2.1-0.3I,0.5+0.2I},{0.4+1.1I,-0.9}};\nassemblyTest = {};\nDo[\n  Do[\n    Module[{oA,oKnown,resid},\n      oA = Oassembled[2,1][st[[1]],st[[2]]][pt[[1]],pt[[2]]];\n      oKnown = O2rot[2,1][st[[1]],st[[2]]][pt[[1]],pt[[2]]];\n      resid = Chop[N[oA-oKnown],10^-9];\n      AppendTo[assemblyTest, {st,pt,resid}]\n    ]\n  ,{pt,gridPts}]\n,{st,statesOf[2,1]}];\nworstAssembly = Max[Abs[assemblyTest[[All,3]]]];\n{\"STEP 3 assembly test (rep (2,1), 6 states x 3 grid points): worst |Oassembled-O2rot|\", worstAssembly,\n \"num cases\", Length[assemblyTest]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1101\" data-out-n=\"546\" data-sub-idx=\"9\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"149\" data-sub-start=\"25\" data-sub-end=\"26\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[546]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqq0254-hc9aks7\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0e1NURVAgMyBhc3NlbWJseSB0ZXN0IChyZXAgKDIsMSksIDYgc3RhdGVzIHggMyBncmlkIHBvaW50cyk6IHdvcnN0IHxPYXNzZW1ibGVkLU8ycm90fH0sMCxcdGV4dHtudW0gY2FzZXN9LDE4XHJpZ2h0XH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">STEP 3 assembly test (rep (2,1), 6 states x 3 grid points): worst |Oassembled-O2rot|</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">num cases</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">18</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[546]= \\left\\{\\text{STEP 3 assembly test (rep (2,1), 6 states x 3 grid points): worst |Oassembled-O2rot|},0,\\text{num cases},18\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "a8123e22-9ab8-408d-a02d-4198a4449f7e"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Full-sweep hard-assert: all 41 states, 6 reps, 2 grid points per state (kept modest for runtime;\n  each point already exercises the FULL B-solve+assembly machinery independently per rep).*)\ngridPts2 = {{1.3,0.7},{2.1-0.3I,0.5+0.2I}};\nassemblyFull = {};\nDo[\n  {λ1,λ2} = rep;\n  Do[\n    Do[\n      Module[{oA,oKnown,resid},\n        oA = Oassembled[λ1,λ2][st[[1]],st[[2]]][pt[[1]],pt[[2]]];\n        oKnown = O2rot[λ1,λ2][st[[1]],st[[2]]][pt[[1]],pt[[2]]];\n        resid = Chop[N[oA-oKnown],10^-9];\n        AppendTo[assemblyFull, {λ1,λ2,st,pt,resid}]\n      ]\n    ,{pt,gridPts2}]\n  ,{st,statesOf[λ1,λ2]}]\n,{rep,{{1,1},{2,1},{1,2},{2,2},{3,1},{1,3}}}];\nworstAssemblyFull = Max[Abs[assemblyFull[[All,5]]]];\nIf[worstAssemblyFull > 10^-8, Abort[]];\n{\"STEP 3 FULL-SWEEP ASSEMBLY CONFIRMED: O[k1,k2] = Σ cA(k1)cB(k2) B-weighted Q-bilinears == O2rot exactly\",\n \"worst deviation\", worstAssemblyFull, \"num states x grid cases\", Length[assemblyFull]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1102\" data-out-n=\"552\" data-sub-idx=\"6\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"150\" data-sub-start=\"19\" data-sub-end=\"20\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[552]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqq02kj-l410x81\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0e1NURVAgMyBGVUxMLVNXRUVQIEFTU0VNQkxZIENPTkZJUk1FRDogT1trMSxrMl0gPSAkXFNpZ21hJCBjQShrMSljQihrMikgQi13ZWlnaHRlZCBRLWJpbGluZWFycyA9PSBPMnJvdCBleGFjdGx5fSxcdGV4dHt3b3JzdCBkZXZpYXRpb259LDAsXHRleHR7bnVtIHN0YXRlcyB4IGdyaWQgY2FzZXN9LDgyXHJpZ2h0XH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">STEP 3 FULL-SWEEP ASSEMBLY CONFIRMED: O[k1,k2] = Σ cA(k1)cB(k2) B-weighted Q-bilinears == O2rot exactly</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">worst deviation</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">num states x grid cases</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">82</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[552]= \\left\\{\\text{STEP 3 FULL-SWEEP ASSEMBLY CONFIRMED: O[k1,k2] = $\\Sigma$ cA(k1)cB(k2) B-weighted Q-bilinears == O2rot exactly},\\text{worst deviation},0,\\text{num states x grid cases},82\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "7c686796-7085-4c94-a6f1-3440b58f3184"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "(*STEP 5 (timeboxed) — structure hunt on B.\n(i) B's diagonal is now known exactly (identified as A^{-1} in Cell 145): B[a,b;a,b] =\nPochhammer[λ1+θ12-b+1,b]/Pochhammer[a+θ12-b+1,b] (reciprocal of Section J's boxed A-diagonal formula).\n(ii)-(iii): analytic derivation first (cheaper than further numeric search), then one numeric check.\nExpanding the naive per-row-insertion candidate Fcand[k1,k2]:=Det[{{br[1][g1],br[1][ug1]},\n{br[2][g2],br[2][ug2]}}]/(g1(θ1)g2(θ2)(θ2-θ1)) with g1=k1^(u/h)Q1,g2=k2^(u/h)Q1 (Section H's\nCandidate 2, no P-insertion) via the SAME residue-sum mechanism as Step 4 gives, exactly:\n  Fcand[k1,k2] = Σ_{s,t} R[s,t]·k1^s k2^t · W[s,t],   R[s,t]:=w1(s)w2(t)(θ2-θ1+(t-s)h)/(θ2-θ1)\ni.e. Fcand's k1^a k2^b MONOMIAL coefficient is the SINGLE term R[a,b]W[a,b] — no mixing across\ndifferent (s,t) splits at the same level. Whereas the CORRECT O[k1,k2] (Step 3) has k1^a k2^b\ncoefficient (-1)^(a+b)/(a!b!)γ_a(λ1)γ_b(λ2)·Σ_{s+t=a+b} B[a,b;s,t]W[s,t] — a genuine LINEAR\nCOMBINATION of every W[s,t] at that level, weighted by the full recoupling row B[a,b;·,·], not just\nthe single \"diagonal\" W[a,b]. This is exactly why Section H's naive per-row-insertion candidates\nfailed: they implicitly assume the (a,b)->(a,b) \"diagonal\" relationship Fcand encodes, but the true\nrelationship is the full B-recoupling. The DIFFERENCE MATRIX is precisely\n  Diff[a,b;s,t] := [(-1)^(a+b)/(a!b!)γ_a(λ1)γ_b(λ2)B[a,b;s,t]] - δ_{s,a}δ_{t,b}·R[a,b]\n— verified numerically below.*)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Numeric confirmation of the Step-5 derivation: compare Fcand[k1,k2] (per-row-insertion,\n  node-normalized so k1=k2 reproduces Step-0's det exactly by construction) against the CORRECT\n  O[k1,k2], coefficient-by-coefficient in k1^a k2^b, for rep (2,1) state (1,0).*)\nClearAll[FcandStepK,RfunStepK];\nRfunStepK[λ1_,λ2_][s_,t_] := w1wt[λ1,λ2][s] w2wt[λ1,λ2][t] (θ2-θ1+(t-s)h)/(θ2-θ1);\nFcandStepK[λ1_,λ2_][M_,n_][k1_,k2_] := Sum[\n  RfunStepK[λ1,λ2][s,t] k1^s k2^t Wval[λ1,λ2][M,n][s,t]\n,{s,0,λ1},{t,0,λ2}];\n(*coefficient-by-coefficient comparison, rep (2,1) state (1,0): O has coeffs at (a,b), Fcand only at\n  (a,b) diagonal (s=a,t=b) — print both and the difference.*)\ncompTable = Table[\n  Module[{oCoef,fCoef},\n    oCoef = (-1)^(a+b)/(a! b!) gammaFun[2,a] gammaFun[1,b] * Module[{srng,bv,idx},\n      {srng,bv} = solveBratM[2,1][a,b][[1;;2]];\n      Sum[bv[[i]] Wval[2,1][1,0][srng[[i]],a+b-srng[[i]]], {i,Length[srng]}]\n    ];\n    fCoef = RfunStepK[2,1][a,b] Wval[2,1][1,0][a,b];\n    {a,b, Chop[N[oCoef],10^-10], Chop[N[fCoef],10^-10], Chop[N[oCoef-fCoef],10^-10]}\n  ]\n,{a,0,2},{b,0,1}];\nFlatten[compTable,1]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
