       "data": "Out[561]= \\left\\{\\text{M matrix (rep (2,1), k1=7/3,k2=5/2)},\\begin{pmatrix}1 & -\\frac{115}{4}\\\\\\frac{259}{12} & \\frac{322}{15}\\\\-\\frac{196}{45} & -\\frac{245}{18}\\end{pmatrix},\\text{MatrixRank},2\\right\\}",
