  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Extra due-diligence check (beyond the fixed 6-rep sweep): does the rank-3 failure generalize to\n  OTHER reps with min(λ1,λ2)>=2, or is it specific to (2,2)? Test rep (2,3) (not in the standard\n  sweep — exercises the full on-demand TauEigensystem/QSolve machinery fresh for this rep).*)\nMtest23 = Mmatrix[2,3][7/3,5/2];\nrank23 = MatrixRank[Mtest23];\ndetM23sym = Det[Mtest23[[1;;3,1;;3]]]; (*3x3 minor, since M is 3x4 here, min dim 3*)\n{\"rep (2,3): M dimensions\", Dimensions[Mtest23], \"rank at sample point\", rank23,\n \"a 3x3 minor determinant (nonzero => rank>=3)\", Chop[detM23sym,10^-10]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1107\" data-out-n=\"572\" data-sub-idx=\"4\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"158\" data-sub-start=\"6\" data-sub-end=\"7\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[572]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqq08zs-2it1zrj\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0e3JlcCAoMiwzKTogTSBkaW1lbnNpb25zfSxcbGVmdFx7Myw0XHJpZ2h0XH0sXHRleHR7cmFuayBhdCBzYW1wbGUgcG9pbnR9LDMsXHRleHR7YSAzeDMgbWlub3IgZGV0ZXJtaW5hbnQgKG5vbnplcm8gPT4gcmFuaz49Myl9LFxmcmFjezE5NTYzOTcwNTQ1fXsxNDA1Njk2fVxyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.4em;vertical-align:-0.95em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">{</span></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">rep (2,3): M dimensions</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">rank at sample point</span></span><span class=\"mp