  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Variant (c): tower on θ2 instead of θ1 (site-ordering asymmetry — recall A,B depended on λ1\n  ONLY, so the \"distinguished\" site for this kind of object might be site 2, not site 1). Test\n  S=λ1+λ2=3 at the SAME sample point, rep (2,1).*)\nClearAll[towerMat2];\ntowerMat2[λ1_,λ2_][S_] := Table[\n  Q1[λ1,λ2][st[[1]],st[[2]]][θ2+s h] / Q1[λ1,λ2][st[[1]],st[[2]]][θ2]\n,{st,statesOf[λ1,λ2]},{s,0,S}];\nMm2 = towerMat2[2,1][3];\nbv2 = N[rhsVec[2,1][7/3,5/2],40];\ncsol2 = LeastSquares[Mm2, bv2];\nresid2 = Max[Abs[Mm2.csol2 - bv2]];\n{\"θ2-tower: dims\", Dimensions[Mm2], \"rank\", MatrixRank[Mm2], \"residual\", resid2}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1112\" data-out-n=\"594\" data-sub-idx=\"7\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"165\" data-sub-start=\"11\" data-sub-end=\"11\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[594]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqq0awx-wt6log8\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0eyRcdGhldGEkMi10b3dlcjogZGltc30sXGxlZnRcezYsNFxyaWdodFx9LFx0ZXh0e3Jhbmt9LDQsXHRleHR7cmVzaWR1YWx9LDI1LjQxNzg4NDYwOTUzNjg5Nzc0MDgwOTNccmlnaHRcfQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord\">2-tower: dims</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">6</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">rank</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">residual</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">25.4178846095368977408093</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
