  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Variant (b), properly tested: multiply (not divide) the TARGET by Q1(θ2) per state before\n  solving against the θ1-tower basis Q1(θ1+sh)/Q1(θ1) — genuinely different linear problem (not a\n  trivial row-rescaling of the original one, since it changes which functional the tower must\n  reproduce). Also try dividing by Q1(θ2) for completeness.*)\nXm0 = towerMat[2,1][3];\nbvBase = N[rhsVec[2,1][7/3,5/2],40];\nq1th2 = N[Table[Q1[2,1][st[[1]],st[[2]]][θ2], {st,statesOf[2,1]}],40];\nbvMult = bvBase q1th2;\nbvDiv  = bvBase / q1th2;\ncsolMult = LeastSquares[Xm0, bvMult];\nresidMult = Max[Abs[Xm0.csolMult - bvMult]];\ncsolDiv = LeastSquares[Xm0, bvDiv];\nresidDiv = Max[Abs[Xm0.csolDiv - bvDiv]];\n{\"multiply by Q1(θ2): residual\", residMult, \"divide by Q1(θ2): residual\", residDiv}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1114\" data-out-n=\"608\" data-sub-idx=\"10\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"167\" data-sub-start=\"13\" data-sub-end=\"13\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[608]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqq0bp9-x57amyx\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0e211bHRpcGx5IGJ5IFExKCRcdGhldGEkMik6IHJlc2lkdWFsfSwxOS43NTcyMjU5MTAwODM0NzkzODEwMjExLFx0ZXh0e2RpdmlkZSBieSBRMSgkXHRoZXRhJDIpOiByZXNpZHVhbH0sMTguMzEwNjA2ODc1Mzk2ODI5NDAzMjA0XHJpZ2h0XH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">multiply by Q1(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord\">2): residual</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">19.7572259100834793810211</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">divide by Q1(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mord\">2): residual</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">18.310606875396829403204</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
