 style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.655em;\"><span style=\"top:-4.815em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">4.04518880433634545024478</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.615em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">8.9288834302921198736014</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-2.415em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">39.3336388826667151011186</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-1.205em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">5.3318082362908496984122</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.155em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.65em;\"><span style=\"top:-4.65em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:6.8em;\"></span><span style=\"width:0.875em;height:4.800em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.875em\" height=\"4.800em\" viewBox=\"0 0 875 4800\"><path d=\"M76,0c-16.7,0,-25,3,-25,9c0,2,2,6.3,6,13c21.3,28.7,42.3,60.3,\n63,95c96.7,156.7,172.8,332.5,228.5,527.5c55.7,195,92.8,416.5,111.5,664.5\nc11.3,139.3,17,290.7,17,454c0,28,1.7,43,3.3,45l0,1209\nc-3,4,-3.3,16.7,-3.3,38c0,162,-5.7,313.7,-17,455c-18.7,248,-55.8,469.3,-111.5,664\nc-55.7,194.7,-131.8,370.3,-228.5,527c-20.7,34.7,-41.7,66.3,-63,95c-2,3.3,-4,7,-6,11\nc0,7.3,5.7,11,17,11c0,0,11,0,11,0c9.3,0,14.3,-0.3,15,-1c5.3,-5.3,10.3,-11,15,-17\nc242.7,-294.7,395.3,-681.7,458,-1161c21.3,-164.7,33.3,-350.7,36,-558\nl0,-1344c-2,