  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*KERNEL CHECK (task step 3), for the r=0 anchor where the system DOES close: is the c_s solution\n  UNIQUE? towerMat[2,1][2] is 6x3 (6 states, 3 unknowns s=0,1,2) — compute its rank; if rank=3 (full\n  column rank), the map is injective and any consistent solution is unique (kernel of the map\n  c->Xc is trivial, matching the exact w1[λ1] match found in Cell 165 with no ambiguity).*)\nrankR0 = MatrixRank[towerMat[2,1][2]];\nnullR0 = NullSpace[towerMat[2,1][2]];\n{\"rank of towerMat[2,1][2] (r=0 anchor, 3 unknowns)\", rankR0,\n \"null space dimension (0 = unique solution)\", Length[nullR0]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"941596\" data-output-id=\"1117\" data-out-n=\"629\" data-sub-idx=\"3\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"170\" data-sub-start=\"6\" data-sub-end=\"7\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[629]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrqq0cvl-ekuhu6t\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0e3Jhbmsgb2YgdG93ZXJNYXRbMiwxXVsyXSAocj0wIGFuY2hvciwgMyB1bmtub3ducyl9LDMsXHRleHR7bnVsbCBzcGFjZSBkaW1lbnNpb24gKDAgPSB1bmlxdWUgc29sdXRpb24pfSwwXHJpZ2h0XH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">rank of towerMat[2,1][2] (r=0 anchor, 3 unknowns)</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">null space dimension (0 = unique solution)</span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
