  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Factor out the COMMON fractional prefactor T^(θ1/h) (from κ1^(u/h)·T^(u/h) evaluated at the\n  θ1-node, same for every state of a rep — tied to θ1 only, not the state) before eliminating, so\n  Resultant sees genuine polynomials.*)\nClearAll[FLpoly];\nFLpoly[λ1_,λ2_][M_,n_][T_] := Simplify[FL[λ1,λ2][M,n][T] / T^(θ1/h)];\n(*smoke: confirm this is now a clean polynomial (no fractional powers of T).*)\nFLpoly[2,1][1,0][T] // Simplify",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
