       "data": "{\n\t\"name\": \"WolframKernelMessage\",\n\t\"message\": \"NSolve::precw: The precision of the argument function ({(14329. - 6305. I) ((-0.9578 + 0.3310 I) + (1.0000 + 0. I) tt) ((-0.3604 + 0.9328 I) + (1.0000 + 0. I) tt)  ((-0.12809 - 0.20204 I) + (1.0000 + 0. I) tt) ((0.46851 - 0.17136 I) + (1.0000 + 0. I) tt)  ((0.7861 - 0.5547 I) + (1.0000 + 0. I) tt)}) is less than WorkingPrecision (40).\",\n\t\"stack\": \"\"\n}",
